    "weight": 8,
    "one_shot": false,
    "text": "An arrow strikes the ground two feet in front of your party. Then a voice from above: clear, unhurried, certain. \"You are at the edge of our land. Turn back.\" A figure stands on a branch overhead. They do not appear to be alone.",
